Author: tornessa
Text: Yes I do. I’m trying so hard at recovery, but all this stress lately is killing me. I don’t want to eat at all. I think I’m going to go back into treatment.

Author: dietfreddo
Text: not ED because i havent really tried to recover but I 1000% know what youre talking about, but with self harm for me. sure i havent relapsed properly but whenever shit goes bad I fantasize about it/plan doing it as comfort and i make risky decisions. tbh i think i partially replaced s/h with fasting/binging. it's like it's my default and it's so easy for my mind to accidentally fall into it (sees razors are on sale --> picks them up --> realize what I'm doing as I put them in my basket --> put them back).
